75
00:03:20,258 --> 00:03:21,378
Peilan, where's Lu Buping?

76
00:03:21,378 --> 00:03:22,417
Why isn't he helping you?

77
00:03:22,617 --> 00:03:23,697
I've told Mother.

78
00:03:23,938 --> 00:03:25,258
Mr. Lu isn't feeling quite well.

79
00:03:26,857 --> 00:03:27,978
He's not feeling well?

80
00:03:28,498 --> 00:03:30,538
So I'm the only one who's all right?

81
00:03:46,417 --> 00:03:47,258
What did you do?

82
00:03:51,098 --> 00:03:52,737
Famous performer Ye Xiaolou

83
00:03:53,378 --> 00:03:54,697
is coming to perform here.

84
00:03:55,177 --> 00:03:56,697
It's packed outside.

85
00:03:57,617 --> 00:03:58,528
Really?

86
00:04:01,417 --> 00:04:02,737
Is your mother free today?

87
00:04:05,897 --> 00:04:06,897
I'm not her.

88
00:04:06,897 --> 00:04:08,177
How would I know if she's free or not?

89
00:04:08,378 --> 00:04:09,498
Why don't you ask her yourself?

90
00:04:10,897 --> 00:04:12,258
Alright. I will ask her.

91
00:04:16,448 --> 00:04:17,538
(Hu Nana)

92
00:04:17,538 --> 00:04:18,417
Cousin.

93
00:04:21,497 --> 00:04:22,458
It's me.

94
00:04:23,978 --> 00:04:24,978
Nana.

95
00:04:25,218 --> 00:04:26,112
A-Sheng.

96
00:04:26,257 --> 00:04:27,817
Nana, what brings you here?

97
00:04:27,978 --> 00:04:28,960
A-Sheng.

98
00:04:31,377 --> 00:04:32,257
Why did you come?

99
00:04:32,257 --> 00:04:34,338
You didn't even inform me beforehand.

100
00:04:35,138 --> 00:04:36,978
I had such a hard time
finding you, A-Sheng.

101
00:04:40,218 --> 00:04:41,218
Take a seat.

102
00:04:41,458 --> 00:04:42,368
Sit.

103
00:04:43,658 --> 00:04:45,218
When I saw you as a child before,

104
00:04:45,218 --> 00:04:47,497
you fell down nine out of ten times.

105
00:04:47,578 --> 00:04:48,898
Who could forget that?

106
00:04:50,057 --> 00:04:50,912
Master.

107
00:05:01,177 --> 00:05:03,177
My cousin. Call her Auntie Hu.

108
00:05:06,297 --> 00:05:07,168
Nana.

109
00:05:08,057 --> 00:05:08,928
This is Banxia.

110
00:05:09,698 --> 00:05:10,658
She is Banxia?

111
00:05:11,098 --> 00:05:12,297
She has grown up.

112
00:05:12,297 --> 00:05:13,216
Hello, Auntie.

113
00:05:13,497 --> 00:05:14,458
Cousin.

114
00:05:14,458 --> 00:05:16,177
We haven't seen each other
for a long time.

115
00:05:16,417 --> 00:05:17,344
Yeah.

116
00:05:17,658 --> 00:05:20,417
It's been over ten years
after you got married.

117
00:05:21,057 --> 00:05:22,297
You've lost weight.

118
00:05:23,698 --> 00:05:24,576
Annoying.

119
00:05:26,177 --> 00:05:27,578
Didn't your husband come with you?

120
00:05:32,417 --> 00:05:33,458
Don't bring it up.

121
00:05:34,698 --> 00:05:35,737
Some years ago,

122
00:05:36,138 --> 00:05:37,057
he passed away.

123
00:05:37,817 --> 00:05:39,617
What illness did he have?

124
00:05:39,617 --> 00:05:41,658
Why didn't you write to me about it?

125
00:05:41,857 --> 00:05:43,098
It was fate.

126
00:05:44,297 --> 00:05:45,417
Fate makes fools of us.

127
00:05:46,898 --> 00:05:47,808
Have some water.

128
00:05:49,658 --> 00:05:50,578
Where are you staying

129
00:05:51,218 --> 00:05:52,218
this time?

130
00:05:53,458 --> 00:05:54,978
I just arrived

131
00:05:55,377 --> 00:05:56,978
and I haven't found a place to stay yet.

132
00:05:57,417 --> 00:05:58,698
I've asked around outside.

133
00:05:58,937 --> 00:06:00,617
All the inns are full.

134
00:06:00,617 --> 00:06:01,978
It isn't a right time.

135
00:06:02,458 --> 00:06:04,497
Ye Xiaolou is performing here.

136
00:06:05,218 --> 00:06:06,138
All are fully booked.

137
00:06:06,218 --> 00:06:07,937
No wonder. It's that dancer, Ye Xiaolou.

138
00:06:09,377 --> 00:06:11,778
So, there's no room available now.

139
00:06:11,778 --> 00:06:12,978
What do I do then?

140
00:06:13,458 --> 00:06:16,297
A few inns in the west of the town
should still have rooms.

141
00:06:16,297 --> 00:06:17,417
Why don't you go check it out?

142
00:06:22,417 --> 00:06:23,538
Alright then.

143
00:06:24,138 --> 00:06:25,458
It's just a bit farther.

144
00:06:25,857 --> 00:06:26,778
Or,

145
00:06:27,297 --> 00:06:29,458
I could find
a run-down temple to stay in.

146
00:06:29,698 --> 00:06:30,658
I'm not afraid.

147
00:06:30,778 --> 00:06:32,937
Although I'm not young anymore,

148
00:06:33,018 --> 00:06:34,698
I am still charming, right?

149
00:06:34,778 --> 00:06:35,737
I believe

150
00:06:35,737 --> 00:06:37,778
