pay attention to me.

151
00:06:37,778 --> 00:06:38,937
Cousin, don't stop me.

152
00:06:38,937 --> 00:06:39,778
I'll go.

153
00:06:39,778 --> 00:06:40,737
I'll just go.

154
00:06:40,737 --> 00:06:41,898
Nonsense.

155
00:06:41,898 --> 00:06:43,937
You will stay in a crappy temple?

156
00:06:44,297 --> 00:06:45,458
Are you kidding me?

157
00:06:45,578 --> 00:06:46,698
What do I do then?

158
00:06:47,297 --> 00:06:48,978
I can't bother you, A-Sheng.

159
00:06:49,817 --> 00:06:51,098
It's not convenient to stay

160
00:06:51,698 --> 00:06:53,098
in the place where you live, right?

161
00:06:58,018 --> 00:07:01,578
What should I do then?

162
00:07:01,578 --> 00:07:02,778
Alright. Alright.

163
00:07:03,857 --> 00:07:05,978
I came here to see a doctor
in the first place

164
00:07:08,257 --> 00:07:09,538
and to visit you by the way.

165
00:07:09,737 --> 00:07:10,978
Now that I knew

166
00:07:11,297 --> 00:07:12,338
