188
00:08:19,698 --> 00:08:21,377
Boss, we are going hunting.

189
00:08:21,458 --> 00:08:23,177
A new hunting ground
is opened outside the town.

190
00:08:23,257 --> 00:08:24,377
Grand opening with grand rewards.

191
00:08:26,177 --> 00:08:27,018
