193
00:08:28,018 --> 00:08:29,257
Call A-Si and go together.

194
00:08:30,218 --> 00:08:31,136
Forget it.

195
00:08:31,617 --> 00:08:32,480
What happened?

196
00:08:34,578 --> 00:08:35,617
