200
00:08:40,458 --> 00:08:41,440
Clean-up?

201
00:08:42,377 --> 00:08:44,857
I grew up. I have to help
my family with some chores.

202
00:08:45,098 --> 00:08:46,617
You guys go ahead.
It's getting dark soon.

203
00:08:46,617 --> 00:08:48,098
I will leave you. I am going to clean.

204
00:08:51,338 --> 00:08:52,288
Buddy.

205
00:08:52,777 --> 00:08:53,728
So, are we going or not?

206
00:08:54,218 --> 00:08:55,978
Yeah.

207
00:08:55,978 --> 00:08:57,218
The arrows are already on our backs.

208
00:09:00,178 --> 00:09:01,257
