218
00:09:26,098 --> 00:09:27,257
That's good.

219
00:09:27,257 --> 00:09:28,160
Where does she live?

220
00:09:28,298 --> 00:09:29,178
She should be around here.

221
00:09:29,578 --> 00:09:30,432
Alright.

222
00:09:30,737 --> 00:09:31,712
Master.

223
00:09:32,338 --> 00:09:33,178
Your sweetheart?

224
00:09:34,458 --> 00:09:35,978
