225
00:09:35,978 --> 00:09:37,617
My cousin. Call her Auntie Hu.

226
00:09:38,257 --> 00:09:39,168
Auntie Hu.

227
00:09:39,897 --> 00:09:41,497
Ruyu's youngest daughter, Keling.

228
00:09:42,298 --> 00:09:43,200
She...

229
00:09:43,698 --> 00:09:45,178
