my mother anymore?

230
00:09:46,978 --> 00:09:48,137
Nonsense.

231
00:09:49,537 --> 00:09:50,657
That's good. I'm relieved.

232
00:09:51,218 --> 00:09:52,578
Auntie Hu, I'm leaving now.

233
00:09:52,578 --> 00:09:53,537
Okay.

234
00:09:55,578 --> 00:09:57,657
