238
00:10:01,418 --> 00:10:02,298
Ruyu should be here.

239
00:10:02,298 --> 00:10:03,232
Okay.

240
00:10:05,298 --> 00:10:06,144
Cousin.

241
00:10:07,058 --> 00:10:07,904
Luckily, you are here.

242
00:10:08,418 --> 00:10:09,418
What are you...

243
00:10:12,978 --> 00:10:14,137
This is...

244
00:10:14,137 --> 00:10:15,617
My cousin. I...

245
00:10:15,938 --> 00:10:16,897
Ruyu,

246
00:10:17,137 --> 00:10:18,080
