247
00:10:19,178 --> 00:10:20,137
I'm Nana.

248
00:10:20,137 --> 00:10:21,120
Nana. Right.

249
00:10:24,257 --> 00:10:25,152
Nana.

250
00:10:27,017 --> 00:10:27,904
Peilan.

251
00:10:29,377 --> 00:10:31,218
Master brought a woman back.

252
00:10:32,137 --> 00:10:33,056
